{
  "stem": "11671.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we decided, kind of spur-of-the-moment, that Harold will go back to Chicago and finish his education and then come back to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So after we came back, it was just a month later that the partition was voted upon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then in April, Israel was established.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you left to come back to America when?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To America.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In October of 1947.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She stayed with the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She stayed with the group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, she stayed with the group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chicago.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we  went--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, my first impression, I thought it was overwhelming, and beautiful, and big.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we arrived in New York, I was-- we were walking across the street, and I started counting how many floors the Empire State Building had.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just made sure I went to see the Statue of Liberty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we children, we read a lot about history.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We, we, we, you know, knew about the Statue of Liberty and what it said on it and all that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I just-- it was very exciting and also very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because when I came here, I could not speak not one single English word.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I had-- we were raised with three languages, like Yiddish, and Hungarian, and Romanian.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we studied Hebrew in school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I learned French, a little French.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I learned German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So when I came here, I knew six languages, and I had to learn another one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was fighting it for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I realized I would just have to-- Harold and I communicated in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, why do I have to learn another language?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you live in America, you learn American.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You learn English.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I studied very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
